-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/billionton-syste-june-sales-fall-14-45-table-6172-tt.html
BILLIONTON SYSTE said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 14.45% to NT$29,082,000 from NT$33,994,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales             29,082           33,994    
YOY%             -14.45%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            169,574          332,901    
YOY%             -49.06% 
=================================================================
 